Scenario : Booking an Airbnb
Description : A tourist wants to book a house on Airbnb app.

object : tourist 
state: name 
behaviour : openapp(), findhouse(),paytheCreditCard()

object : app
state : list of all the available houses, features
behaviour : DisplayHouse(), acceptthepayment()

object : house
state: price, location 
behaviour : gettheprice(), getthelocation()

object : CreditCard
state : amount, card number 

class tourist{
string location;
